{"tid":286870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黎姿提早為李嘉欣慶祝47歲生日: 我真係恭喜你呀","createTime":"2017-06-17T03:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T11:10:56.000Z","uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a546a9c5eea04f38cf29a9d3b03b3c7fb094f690","tid":286870,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"下周二，即係20號係大美人李嘉欣嘅47歲生日，不過Michelle喺踏入生日月冇耐，已經喺微博留言叫大家唔好送禮物，佢話：「每年收到的禮物和祝福都讓我很感動，踏入了生日的月份，『禮物』意義是分享喜悅和愛，如果你正打算送我禮物的話，請考慮支持『Ukulele 暑假班眾贈行動』，給自閉症兒童一個難忘的夏天！」<br />\n<br />\n生日都不忘做善事，真係好愛心，查實有時唔一定收禮物先開心，同埋一班朋友見吓面，食個飯已經好開心，Michelle嘅好友黎姿，噚日喺微博貼咗啲食飯相，同場仲有Michelle嘅家姐李嘉明與及設計師好友張潔雯，齊齊同好友慶祝生日，睇見佢哋個個樣都冇乜點變，都係凍齡美魔女，真係好葡萄囉！之後黎姿都留言話：「Happy birthday to 大美人祝永遠美麗、健康、喜樂常在！我真係恭喜你呀！」Michelle亦轉發微博話：「謝謝你們美美的祝福！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/112702_cc752a7b0d3bf2a0db875615851d7932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F112702_cc752a7b0d3bf2a0db875615851d7932.jpg&h=6d2ddd13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/112704_2e343d98231328cd5591d78b9737fba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F112704_2e343d98231328cd5591d78b9737fba1.jpg&h=56ee224c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/112705_bdadf7c289d7d77d4672263f0b8dcec4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F112705_bdadf7c289d7d77d4672263f0b8dcec4.jpg&h=35d6d684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf729182d5ccb17fc1b21555692e920e84ee833c","tid":286870,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T19:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝GiGi 美美的祝福<br />\n<br />\n希望連登仔唔好再誹謗佢老爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54a989491b8827cc5399f93276640a9798d4f27","tid":286870,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T19:50:28.000Z","msg":"打工仔黎咋"},{"pid":"ca6853ccd85bb2942ce03a95531d50ff0acfeb29","tid":286870,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打工仔黎咋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打工仔？打工仔你使對人咁好個呵？"},{"pid":"768c1a6d800920a9b0be511a9a43ab96381fe41d","tid":286870,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"Gigi真係寫「我真係恭喜你呀」？"}]}